[
    {
        "content": "<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>I am working on HID bindings and a driver as documented here: <a href=\"https://binary-eater.github.io/tags/usb-monitor-control/\">https://binary-eater.github.io/tags/usb-monitor-control/</a></p>\n<p>I have this macro.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[macro_export]</span>\n<span class=\"fm\">macro_rules!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">usb_device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">vendor</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$($vendor</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">expr</span><span class=\"p\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">product</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$($product</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">expr</span><span class=\"p\">))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">DeviceId</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Opaque</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">hid_device_id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">bus</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mh\">0x3</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cm\">/* BUS_USB */</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">vendor</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$($vendor</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">product</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$($product</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"c1\">// SAFETY: The rest is zeroed out to initialize `struct hid_device_id`,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"c1\">// sets `Option&lt;&amp;F&gt;` to be `None`.</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$crate</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">mem</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">MaybeUninit</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">hid_device_id</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">zeroed</span><span class=\"p\">().</span><span class=\"n\">assume_init</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}))</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>which leads to this error</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"cp\">$vendor</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">expr</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">followed</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">which</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">allowed</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">expr</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">fragments</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">hid</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">157</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">38</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n<span class=\"mi\">157</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">vendor</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$($vendor</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">expr</span><span class=\"p\">);</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">product</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$($product</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">expr</span><span class=\"p\">))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                                      </span><span class=\"o\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">allowed</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">after</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">expr</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">fragments</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">note</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">allowed</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">there</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">are</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">or</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"err\">`</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>My goal was to do something along the lines of this pattern.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">module_hid_driver</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">driver</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">HidMonitorControl</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">id_table</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">hid</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">usb_device</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">vendor</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mh\">0x0955</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">product</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mh\">0x7214</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">},</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"monitor-control\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">author</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"Rahul Rameshbabu &lt;sergeantsagara@protonmail.com&gt;\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">description</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"Driver for the USB Monitor Control Class\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">license</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"GPL\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 502918772,
        "sender_full_name": "Rahul Rameshbabu",
        "timestamp": 1740963662
